{"word":"G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁράω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">horáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hor-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண்பி, எச்சரிக்கையாயிரு, பார், காண், தரிசி"},{"paragraph":"to see to, look to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Properly to <i>stare</i> at (compare <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>), that is, (by implication) to <i>discern</i> clearly (physically or mentally); by extension to <i>attend</i> to; by Hebraism to <i>experience</i>; passively to <i>appear:</i> - behold, perceive, see, take heed.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2300/2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2334/2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529/2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705/3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706/3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707/3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708/3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308/4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517/517\">G517</a>"}]}